{"word":"G4103 - πιστός - pistós - pis-tos' - Believe","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">πιστός</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">pistós</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">pis-tos'</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Believe</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Adjective / பெயரடை</span>"},{"paragraph":"உண்மையான, உண்மையுள்ள, நிச்சயமான, விசுவாசமுள்ள - பெயரடை"},{"paragraph":"1. trusty, faithful"},{"paragraph":"2. easily persuaded; believing, confiding, trusting"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G3982 - πείθω - peíthō - pi'-tho/3982\">G3982</a>; objectively <i>trustworthy</i>; subjectively <i>trustful:</i> - believe (-ing, -r), faithful (-ly), sure, true.</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G3640/3640\">G3640</a>, <a href=\"#/G4100/4100\">G4100</a>, <a href=\"#/G4102/4102\">G4102</a>, <a href=\"#/G4103/4103\">G4103</a>, <a href=\"#/G4104/4104\">G4104</a>, <a href=\"#/G569/569\">G569</a>, <a href=\"#/G570/570\">G570</a>, <a href=\"#/G571/571\">G571</a>"}]}